parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the intermediate steering shaft can cause loss of power steering, making it difficult to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: Clunking
knocking
or popping noise when turning the steering wheel
loss of power steering
stiff or tight steering
difficulty turning the wheel
and feeling of the steering wheel "binding" or "catching".

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause loss of power steering, making it difficult to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: Loss of power steering
stiff or tight steering
difficulty turning the wheel
and feeling of the steering wheel "binding" or "catching".

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sun visor can obstruct the driver's vision, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The sun visor hangs down and will not return to the upright position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The paint peeling and defect can lead to rust and corrosion, affecting the vehicle's overall appearance and resale value.
symptoms: The paint on the roof is peeling off
and the paint failure has progressed to include nearly every panel on the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power liftgate motor arm can cause the hatch to fall on occupants, leading to injury or accidents.
symptoms: The power liftgate motor arm detaches from the upper portion of the rear door
and the hole to screw becomes stripped over time.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rear Hatch Door and Window Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear hatch door and window can cause accidents or injuries, especially if the door opens or closes unexpectedly while the vehicle is in motion.
symptoms: The rear hatch door and window do not close or open properly
and the door may open or close unexpectedly while the vehicle is in motion.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the moon roof can cause water to leak into the vehicle, leading to mold, mildew, and electrical issues.
symptoms: The moon roof is leaking
and the vehicle's floor is wet
causing mold and mildew to grow.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the window and door can cause accidents or injuries, especially if the window falls off the track or the door does not close properly.
symptoms: The window is off the track and unable to roll up
and the door does not close or open properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver-side sun visor can obstruct the driver's vision, causing a safety hazard and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The sun visor sticks in the down position
fails to stay up
or falls down suddenly
blocking the driver's view; the visor has a delayed or incomplete return to its normal position; the visor has a sudden loss of pressure or resistance.
